modName: Enrond Half-Elven- Level 15 high elf mage
summary: This is a small file with my level 15 High elf mage just after he has beaten the main story line and got out of Sovnguard.
descriptionHtml:
Destruction at 60
Restoration 24
Speech 22
Sneak 40
One hand 22
Heavy armor 19
Light armor 19
Smithing 15
Enchanting 77



No side quests done. Only the one where you have to steal the ring to get Brynjolf to talk to you is done.

All collage of winterhold main quests done.

All main story quests done

2 Dragon Priest masks. Nahkriin and Morokai

The staff of magnus is in the invintory.

Whiterun house bought and fully decorated.

11.5K gold

25 dragon bones and about 19 dragon scales in the chest in the house



You start up on the throte of the world so all you have to do is fast travel to White run and be on your way.

The only main cities i havent been to yet are Markarth and Dawnstar.


Enjoy :D
author: Morokai the almighty
